程序包 org.diku.dms.bds_project

类 Graph<VD,​ED>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.diku.dms.bds_project.Graph<VD,​ED>
  • 类型参数:
    VD - vertex attribute data type
    ED - edge attribute data type
    所有已实现的接口:
    java.io.Serializable
    public class Graph<VD,​ED>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Graph consists of three RDDs: `VertexRDD`, `EdgeRDD` and `EdgeTripletRDD`. `vertices` contains a collection of vertices. `edges` contains a collection of edges. `edgeTriplets` is something that combines `vertices` and `edges`, which has vertex attributes on edges.
